headline: Pool Corporation Declares Quarterly Cash Dividend
summary: COVINGTON, La., Feb. 26, 2025 -- Pool Corporation announced today that its Board of Directors declared a quarterly cash dividend of $1.20 per share. The dividend will be payable on March 26,...
